[V] — a 1D vector
[M] — a matrix #type:2D

[L]: length of [V]
[R]: result
[L]: length of [V] = 0
[Y]: a color = Red

/add [A]: an integer, [B]: an integer
	[>] [A] + [B]

/subtract
[A]: an integer, [B]: an integer
	[1] — [A] - [B]
	[>] [1]

[*] this is a general comment
that spans multiple lines
and keeps going

[1] — add[ [V], [M] ]
[^] call add with V and M

[!] — done processing
